snippet.title: [DOAXVV] New Venus Release! Introducing Shandy
snippet.description:
○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com/en/lp.html
Shandy has finally come to "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!" (Voice: Shino Shimoji)
Shandy, the mysterious and glamorous bartender, 
comes to the island in search of some stimulation.
Enjoy a vacation with Shandy, the new Venus who isn't afraid of teasing the Boss.


○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam,Johren) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：Steam 10 April 2019 (Wednesday), Johren 1 July 2021 (Thursday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in Steam,Johren
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
